Privacy Policy
Last Updated: June 20, 2023

We appreciate your choice of our game "Tetris". Your privacy is very important to us, and we are committed to protecting your information. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and store your information when you use our game. Please read this policy carefully to understand our practices and principles.

1. Information We Collect
1.1 Personal Information
We do not knowingly collect personal information that can be used to identify you as an individual, such as your name, email address, or phone number. However, if you voluntarily provide such information through support requests or other channels, we may use it only to provide the requested services.

1.2 Non-Personal Information
We may collect non-personal information that does not identify you as an individual. This information may include:

Technical Information: Your device type, model, operating system, OS version, unique device identifiers, browser type, and other technical data.
Usage Information: Data about your use of our game, such as game progress, levels played, playtime, and other gameplay metrics.
2. Use of Information
We use the collected information for the following purposes:

Improving and Optimizing the Game: We analyze usage data to improve the gaming experience, identify and fix bugs, enhance game performance, and refine the user interface.
Analytics: We use the information to analyze game metrics, study trends, and understand our players' preferences.
Security and Protection: We may use the information to detect and prevent fraud, abuse, and violations of our terms of use.
3. Sharing Information
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except as required for:

Compliance with Legal Requirements: We may disclose information in response to legal requests or court orders.
Security Assurance: We may disclose information to protect the rights, property, or safety of our company, our users, or others.
4. Information Security
We implement various security measures to protect your information. This includes the use of encryption, secure servers, network protective mechanisms, and restricting access to information only to authorized personnel.

5. Children's Access
Our game is accessible to users of all ages, including children. We are particularly concerned about protecting children's privacy. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13 without verifiable parental consent. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child without proper consent, we will immediately delete such information.

6. Cookies and Similar Technologies
We may use cookies and similar technologies to collect information about your activity in the game. This helps us understand your preferences and settings and improve our services. You can control the use of cookies through your browser or device settings.

7. Changes to the Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the updated policy on this page. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy regularly to stay informed about any changes.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or about protecting your information, please contact us at: kirillprilipko20@gmail.com.
